summarized_story:
The President, Muhammadu Buhari, has arrived in Kano for the wedding ceremony of his son, Yusuf Buhari, who is getting married to Zahra Bayero, the daughter of Nasiru Ado Bayero, the Emir of Bichi in Kano State.
The wedding will be taking place today at the palace of the Emir of Bichi.
